00:37:19,300 --> 00:37:21,100
Who is looking for Judge Wu Qili?

793
00:37:21,590 --> 00:37:22,460
Hello, it's us.

794
00:37:22,570 --> 00:37:23,330
It's you.

795
00:37:23,670 --> 00:37:25,960
We're Xu Jianshe's lawyers.

796
00:37:26,440 --> 00:37:28,350
Didn't you submit your defense opinions?

797
00:37:28,350 --> 00:37:29,120
What else?

798
00:37:29,680 --> 00:37:31,640
Please let Judge Wu know again

799
00:37:31,670 --> 00:37:33,270
that we wish to meet with him.

800
00:37:33,310 --> 00:37:34,750
We want to present our opinions on this case

801
00:37:34,750 --> 00:37:36,090
to him.

802
00:37:36,910 --> 00:37:37,880
Don't worry.

803
00:37:37,910 --> 00:37:38,570
The judge will

804
00:37:38,570 --> 00:37:40,490
carefully study your defense.

805
00:37:40,720 --> 00:37:42,760
You'll see it once the verdict is announced.

806
00:37:42,760 --> 00:37:43,670
Your opinions will

807
00:37:43,670 --> 00:37:45,280
be reflected in the verdict.

808
00:37:45,400 --> 00:37:46,110
I'm sorry.

809
00:37:46,130 --> 00:37:48,440
Our client was sentenced to life in the first instance.

810
00:37:48,440 --> 00:37:50,420
We believe there is a significant issue.

811
00:37:50,420 --> 00:37:51,830
So we want to

812
00:37:51,850 --> 00:37:54,310
express our opinions to the Judge in person.

813
00:37:54,690 --> 00:37:57,160
Please tell the judge.

814
00:37:57,200 --> 00:37:59,000
We won't take up much of his time.

815
00:37:59,450 --> 00:38:00,870
I'm sorry. Judge Wu is in session.

816
00:38:00,870 --> 00:38:02,340
He really doesn't have time.

817
00:38:02,340 --> 00:38:03,460
Please leave.

818
00:38:09,270 --> 00:38:10,470
I don't want to leave.

819
00:38:10,870 --> 00:38:12,240
I think reading words

820
00:38:12,270 --> 00:38:13,970
is different from hearing them.

821
00:38:13,970 --> 00:38:15,060
Let's wait.

822
00:38:15,090 --> 00:38:15,580
Okay.

823
00:38:24,070 --> 00:38:25,160
Judge Liu is available.

824
00:38:25,160 --> 00:38:25,850
Come with me.

